<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>$this-&gt;view-&gt;dojo()-&gt;requireModule('dojo.NodeList-fx');</p>

<p>causes</p>

<p>exception 'Zend_Dojo_View_Exception' with message 'Module name specified, "dojo.NodeList-fx", contains invalid characters'</p>

<p>The NodeList-fx module is, however, spelled that way, so we should be able to load it using requireModule.</p>

